Step 1:  git clone https: https://github.com/elc-digital/sp-sre-deployment-controller-service.git
https://github.com/elc-digital/sp-sre-deployment-controller-service/tree/dcs-aad
Step 2:  cd sp-sre-deployment-controller-service/
Step 3:  ls
Step 4:  git checkout dcs-aad
Step 5:  git pull
Step 6:  git checkout -b ELCSRE-40927 dcs-aad     #Please give the Jira ticket number for the DCS Updation.
Step 6.1: cd configs/
Step 6.2: cd project-config/
Step 7:  ls 
              AM/     APAC/       UK/        #Please select the region you are going to update
Step 8:  cd APAC
Step 9:  vi <spinnaker-project-configs-apac.yml>      #Check for the configs yaml file
ESC :/SPINAKKERAPPNAME 7YY P 
Step 10: Edit the selected file
         i) :se nu    # for numbers
         ii)/<PIP-NP>  /Frontier  #search for the project 
         iii) If it is a new application:
              need to copy from application name i.e., around 15 lines for 3 env
              shortcut: press <No.of lines need to copy>yy  
                         ex: 15yy
         iv) Paste at the end of the application 
             shortcut: press p
         v) edit and save the changes in the file
Step 11:  git diff
Step 12:  git add spinnaker-project-configs-am.yml
Step 13:  cd ../../..                         # come to the sre-deployment-controller-service
Step 14:  git commit -m "ELCSRE-40927"            #Please give the Jira ticket number for the DCS Updation.
Step 15:  git push origin ELCSRE-40927            #Please give the Jira ticket number for the DCS Updation.
Step 16:  Now the Dcs is updated
Step 17:  Create a pull request and merge request in the Github - branch to dcsaad
Step 18:  run the jenkins job in specific region(am,apac,uk)
SRE-->SREPORTAL-->sre-deployment-controller-service-update-config-github
https://jenkins.am.sre.elcompanies.com/job/SRE/job/SRE-Portal/job/sre-deployment-controller-service-update-config-github/ -->  Build parameter --> docker push set it as True 
Step 19:  Collect the new image tag                #Docker image tag: [v20211208-113313-35085e9db04b061806b8e061873618ac2315e1f6]
Step 20:  change the tag in
          i) If Test Portal/ Non-Prod
https://bitbucket.elcompanies.net/projects/SREDNP/repos/sdc-sre-non-prod/browse?at=refs%2Fheads%2Fsre-dcs-test
          ii) If Prod SRE portal
https://bitbucket.elcompanies.net/projects/SREDP/repos/sdc-sre-platform-prod/browse?at=refs%2Fheads%2Fsre-dcs-prod
Step 21:  Go to the Spinnaker <AM> region or APAC
          search for "sredcs" application
          i) If Test Portal/ Non-Prod   - execute pl-sre-dcs-test-aad
          ii) If Prod SRE portal        - execute pl-sre-dcs-prod-aad
Step 22:  After successful execution check and confirm in the respective portals.
 
:se nu      ---> to get the line numbers
